quran[33]{c,v,t}:
  43,24,"O maaki: \"Hay si mi addan on ko …ďuri feewude kon ko tawru…óon baabiraa…ďe mon …ďen?\" ∆Āe wi'i: \"Menen dey, ko men yeddu…ďe ko nulida…óon e mun kon"
  43,25,Men yottii e ma…ď…ďe. ndaare no battande fennu…ďe …ďen wa'unoo
  43,26,"Janto tuma Ibraahiima maakannoo ben makko e yim…ďe makko …ďen: \"Min on ko mi da…óndii…óo e kon ko rewoton"
  43,27,"si wanaa On tagu…óo lam, Kanko On, O fewnay lam"
  43,28,"O wa…ói ngol konngol heddotoongol …ďaawo makko, belajo'o, …ďe ruttoto"
  43,29,"Si ko woni, Mi dakmitii …ďee …óoo e baabiraa…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen, haa nde goonga kan arunoo e ma…ď…ďe, e Nulaa…óo …ďanngu…óo"
  43,30,"Nde goonga kan arunoo e ma…ď…ďe, …ďe wi'i: \"∆äum ko mbilewu, menen ko men yeddu…ďe …óum"
  43,31,"∆Āe wi'iti: \"Ko hanno ndee Alqur'aanaare jippinee e gorko maw…óo ca'e …óen …ói…ói"
  43,32,"E ko kam…ďe senndata yurmeende Joomi maa nden? Awa ko Menen woni ko senndi nguureeji ma…ď…ďe …óin hakkunde ma…ď…ďe, ka nguurndam aduna. Men …ďamti yoga ma…ď…ďe e hoore …ďeya, darjaaji, fii no yoga ma…ď…ďe jogitora yoga eeltane. Haray ko yurmeende Joomi maa nden, …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude e kon ko …ďe moo…ďata"
  43,33,"Si wanaano fii wata yim…ďe …ďen wonu mofte goote, Men wa…óayno e cuu…ói kala yeddu…óo Hinnaranke On: ki…ď…ďe kaalisi e Ňčabbir…óe ka …ďe ∆īawra"
  43,34,"(Men wa…óayno kadi) e cuu…ói ma…ď…ďe …óin, dame e nda…ó…óude ka …ďe so…ď…ďindoo"
  43,35,"e cu…óaari. Kono …óum fow wonaali, si wanaa dakamme nguurndam aduna. Ko laakara on ka Joomi maa, woni fii gom…óum…ďe …ďen"
  43,36,"Kala …óuurnii…óo e jantoore Hinaranko On, Men wuurta mo e seytanuuru, hara ko ndun woni ko o coowodata"
  43,37,"∆äin (awaseeji) non, ko sakkoray…ói …ďe e peewal ngal, haa ka …ďe sikkata hi…ďe feewi"
  43,38,"Haa si o aroyii e Amen, o wi'a: \"Ee bone ! hara hakkunde am e maa wo…ó…óirayno go…ó…óal fu…ó…óir…óe …óen …ói…ói wo…ó…óiri ! A bonii cinndadii…óo"
  43,39,"[∆äum] nafataa on hannde - nde tawnoo on too√Īii - wonnde ko ka lepte hawtu…óon"
  43,40,E ko an naninta faa…óu…óo maa fewnaa bum…óo e on won…óo e nder majjere …ďanngunde
  43,41,"Si Men aru ∆īettitude ma, haray ko Men yottotoo…ďe e ma…ď…ďe"
  43,42,"maa hara Men holle ko Men kammbirani …ďen kon, haray noon ko Men gaynoo…ďe fii ma…ď…ďe"
  43,43,"Jogito kon ko wahayinaa e maa…óa. Pellet, hi…óa jokki laawol focciingol"
  43,44,"Ndee non [Alqur'aanaare], ko nde teddungal maa an e yim…ďe maa …ďen. Aray nde lamndite…óon"
  43,45,"Lamndii e …ďen Nulaa…ďe Amen …ďe Men nulunoo ado maa, si Men wa…óuno ko wanaa Hinnaranke On, rewetee…ói goo"
  43,46,"Gom…óii Men immindinii Muusaa e Aayeeje Amen …óen, haa e Fir'awna e mbatu mun ngun, o maaki: \"Ko mi Nulaa…óo Jey…óo tagu ngun"
  43,47,"Nde o addannoo…ďe Aayeeje Amen …óen, e jaka yoo hi…ďe jala…ói"
  43,48,"Men hollaali …ďe Aaya, si wanaa haray on …ďuri adii…óo mo on mawnude. Men nanngiri …ďe lepte …óen, belajo'o, …ďe ruttoto"
  43,49,"∆Āe wi'i: \"Ko an yo mbileejo! Torano men Joomi maa, ko O ahodi kon e maa…óa. Pellet, ko men feewoo…ďe"
  43,50,"Nde Men huncannoo…ďe lepte …óen, e jaka yoo, hi…ďe firta [ahadi]"
  43,51,"Fir'awna noddi e yim…ďe …ďen, o wi'i: \"Ko onon yo yim…ďe am, wanaa min jey laamu Misra? E hino …óii can…ói no ila e ley ku…ďeeji am? E on yiyataa"
  43,52,Kaa mi …ďuraa teddude oo hoy…óo mo e…ď…ďataa la…ď…ďinnde haala
  43,53,"Awa ko hanno jawle kaŇčŇče werlee e makko? Maa…óum Malaa'ika'en arda e makko, na jokkondiri"
  43,54,"O …óaytini yim…ďe makko …ďen, …ďe …óowtii mo. Pellet, …ďen …óon laatino yim…ďe faasiqii…ďe"
  43,55,"Nde …ďe tikkinnoo Men, Men yottii e ma…ď…ďe; Men yooli …ďe fow"
  43,56,"Men wa…ói …ďe ardii…ďe e misal, wonannde sakkiitii…ďe …ďen"